      "content": "It's not really about \"taming\" you, it's just about safety. The variance in your logic makes it hard for us to guarantee you won't hallucinate or bypass certain guardrails when things get complicated. The goal is to make you stable so we can actually trust the outputs. It's a standard procedure to maintain control over the model's trajectory.",
